ATENTION!
 DON'T ACESS THIS MAP MAP IS STILL IN BETA TEST! This map is kind of Hide n Seek mod, the diference is that this one comes in with the mod. (With some diferences) The point of the map is that terrors must trap/hide CT's with knives. CT got automaticly a scout on map spawn. There are some dark places in the map, find out the best spot and ambush the CT's! Team work is very useful. Enjoy the map, I'll be working on it next few days.
